        public Connection.KeyVal contentType​(String contentType)
        Description copied from interface: Connection.KeyVal
        Set the Content Type header used in the MIME body (aka mimetype) when uploading files. Only useful if Connection.KeyVal.inputStream(InputStream) is set.
